581
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,960
back yet?

582
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:25,359
Call them

583
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,559
and rush the cake.

584
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,119
It's not a birthday if there is no

585
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,039
cake and birthday wishes.

586
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:29,960
I called. It's downstairs.

587
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,160
I make a wish every year.

588
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:31,960
It never comes true anyway.

589
00:17:33,039 --> 00:17:34,279
That's exactly what I like

590
00:17:34,359 --> 00:17:35,160
about Wenwen.

591
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:37,640
She doesn't sweat the small stuff.

592
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:39,039
A kid raised by Yu Ming and Yitong

593
00:17:39,119 --> 00:17:40,279
is bound to

594
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:41,319
be unique.

595
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:43,480
That's right. Exactly.

596
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:44,240
Wenwen,

597
00:17:44,359 --> 00:17:45,119
next year

598
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,960
we're planning to move
into a bigger place.

599
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,400
When your birthday comes around,

600
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:50,000
come celebrate at our house, okay?

601
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,440
No, thanks.

602
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:53,079
Wenwen has celebrated

603
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,440
every birthday here
since she was born.

604
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:05,839
Yu Ming,

605
00:18:06,359 --> 00:18:07,599
warm up some wine for me.

606
00:18:07,799 --> 00:18:09,759
At my age, I can't
drink it cold anymore.

607
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,440
Yitong,

608
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:12,880
does your travel agency

609
00:18:13,079 --> 00:18:13,880
have any family route

610
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,880
for the New Year?

611
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,000
Where would you go?

612
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:16,920
Europe, probably.

613
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:18,880
Zihan's growing up.

614
00:18:19,079 --> 00:18:19,799
Weijie said

615
00:18:20,000 --> 00:18:21,359
he wants to take him around

616
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,400
to see more of the world.

617
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,880
Take our boy to Iceland

618
00:18:24,119 --> 00:18:25,240
see the Blue Lagoon,

619
00:18:26,079 --> 00:18:26,720
the Golden Circle,

620
00:18:27,039 --> 00:18:27,799
the black sand beaches,

621
00:18:27,839 --> 00:18:28,480
and maybe see whales.

622
00:18:28,799 --> 00:18:29,160
Okay?

623
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:30,640
We don't really have that route.

624
00:18:31,079 --> 00:18:32,119
But if you're going to Northern Europe,

625
00:18:32,119 --> 00:18:33,440
you might as well do all five countries.

626
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,920
And if you like it,

627
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,680
you could settle there.

628
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:36,160
Right?

629
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:36,559
Sounds great.

630
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:37,559
Then forget

631
00:18:37,559 --> 00:18:38,680
travel agencies.

632
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,079
We'll do it ourselves.

633
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:41,599
Sure.

634
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,119
Yitong.

635
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,519
Let's go together then.

636
00:18:44,799 --> 00:18:46,359
We'll see.

637
00:18:46,359 --> 00:18:47,960
It depends on the timing.

638
00:18:48,039 --> 00:18:49,880
Wenwen will probably
be in her tutoring classes.

639
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:50,559
Maybe next time.

640
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,279
It's hot!

641
00:18:51,519 --> 00:18:51,960
Careful!

642
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:53,319
And when exactly is "next time"?

643
00:18:53,519 --> 00:18:54,079
Yu Ming,

644
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,640
Wenwen's grown up now.

645
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,400
She remembers

646
00:18:56,519 --> 00:18:57,319
everything you say.

647
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:58,279
If you can't keep your promise,

648
00:18:58,599 --> 00:18:59,400
she'll be heartbroken.

649
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:00,720
Right, Wenwen?

650
00:19:02,319 --> 00:19:03,359
That Kui guy... what's his name?

651
00:19:03,519 --> 00:19:04,200
Hong Jinkui.

652
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,640
Right. That fat man.

653
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,000
He owes you a fortune.

654
00:19:07,039 --> 00:19:07,920
Over 200,000 yuan, isn't it?

655
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:08,960
If you could collect

656
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:09,559
that money back,

657
00:19:09,599 --> 00:19:10,880
you could take Wenwen
on a nice trip too.

658
00:19:11,119 --> 00:19:12,359
I-I'm trying to find him.

659
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,400
Yu Ming.

660
00:19:13,839 --> 00:19:15,240
You're not a kid anymore.

661
00:19:15,359 --> 00:19:16,640
Act like a responsible adult.

662
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:18,680
Stop jumping from one thing to another

663
00:19:18,680 --> 00:19:19,599
all over the place.

664
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:20,720
You're almost forty.

665
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:22,440
And your pockets
are emptier than your face is.

666
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:22,920
How is that okay?

667
00:19:23,240 --> 00:19:24,240
What about your parents?

668
00:19:24,559 --> 00:19:25,799
What about Wenwen's education?

669
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,480
I heard you two are even thinking

670
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,400
about having another child.

671
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:29,759
Honey,

672
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:31,480
your wine is warmed up.

673
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,680
Drink it.

674
00:19:32,839 --> 00:19:34,440
Stop talking. Stop talking.

675
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:37,000
Ming,

676
00:19:37,119 --> 00:19:38,039
Listen to me.

677
00:19:38,119 --> 00:19:39,119
You’ve got to be steady

678
00:19:39,119 --> 00:19:40,279
in your life.

679
00:19:40,599 --> 00:19:42,559
Nobody becomes fat from a single bite.

680
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:44,000
You have to take it step by step.

681
00:19:44,160 --> 00:19:45,240
Move forward steadily.

682
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:47,079
Look at our young couple.

683
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:48,559
They both work at the bank,

684
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:50,039
holding solid jobs.

685
00:19:52,119 --> 00:19:53,480
They've got a decent standing

686
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,920
in society now.

687
00:19:55,039 --> 00:19:56,039
And you're satisfied with that?

688
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:57,200
That's not enough.

689
00:19:57,279 --> 00:19:58,200
You've got to move up.

690
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,160
Higher and higher.

691
00:20:01,599 --> 00:20:02,680
You motherless fool.

692
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,160
Your mother is my mother.

693
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:10,440
And my mother is your mother.

694
00:20:14,079 --> 00:20:14,759
I'm done eating.

695
00:20:16,799 --> 00:20:17,359
All this food

696
00:20:17,359 --> 00:20:18,440
can't keep you quiet?

697
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:21,559
Hello, delivery.

698
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,480
Okay, thank you.

699
00:20:24,559 --> 00:20:24,839
Thanks.

700
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,640
Mom, I'll get it.

701
00:20:25,839 --> 00:20:26,440
I've got it.

702
00:20:27,519 --> 00:20:28,319
Wenwen,

703
00:20:28,599 --> 00:20:29,720
the cake is here.

704
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,680
Come on. Be a good girl and come out.

705
00:20:31,960 --> 00:20:33,599
Everyone's going to sing
Happy Birthday to you.

706
00:20:33,799 --> 00:20:35,000
Then we'll cut the cake,

707
00:20:35,119 --> 00:20:36,640
blow out the candles, and make a wish.

708
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:37,640
Come on, sweetheart.

709
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:38,799
Wenwen?

710
00:20:39,079 --> 00:20:40,000
The older the kids,

711
00:20:40,279 --> 00:20:41,759
the worse their temper.

712
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,680
This whole family...

713
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:44,240
The elders don't act like elders,

714
00:20:44,359 --> 00:20:45,599
and the kids don't act like kids.

715
00:20:45,759 --> 00:20:46,480
We came here

716
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:48,039
to celebrate her birthday,

717
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,039
and now what?

718
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,000
They're giving us attitude

719
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,119
for no reason.

720
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:51,920
Who raised them like this?

721
00:20:52,160 --> 00:20:52,799
Exactly.

722
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:53,960
If Zihan ever acted like that,

723
00:20:54,079 --> 00:20:54,640
Weijie would've...

724
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:55,640
That's enough!

725
00:20:56,039 --> 00:20:58,079
Of course your son is amazing.

726
00:20:58,279 --> 00:20:59,720
Your son is amazing.

727
00:20:59,759 --> 00:21:02,119
Collecting subsidies,
collecting benefits,

728
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,519
and knowing how to butter people up.

729
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:04,400
Let me tell you.

730
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,680
If Yu Feng were still alive,

731
00:21:05,839 --> 00:21:07,279
none of you would matter.

732
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:08,880
Lanying,

733
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:10,160
that's not fair.

734
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,039
That's just not right.

735
00:21:11,279 --> 00:21:12,599
Yu Feng, Yu Feng, Yu Feng.

736
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,000
You know where he is.

737
00:21:14,079 --> 00:21:15,559
He's in the photo frame now.

738
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:16,400
You know that, right?

739
00:21:23,519 --> 00:21:25,000
What are you even talking about?

740
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,359
I'll say whatever I want.

741
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,079
I’ll say it anyway.

742
00:21:27,079 --> 00:21:27,839
Enough!

743
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:34,839
That's enough.

744
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,920
Every single family gathering

745
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,759
ends the same way.

746
00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:59,799
Don't get too discouraged.

747
00:22:07,559 --> 00:22:08,640
When can we have a baby?

748
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:13,039
Today,

749
00:22:14,680 --> 00:22:16,079
I was late because

750
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,960
I went to buy you a pair of shoes.

751
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:21,880
Try them on.

752
00:22:24,079 --> 00:22:24,920
I'm asking you, Yu Ming.

753
00:22:25,319 --> 00:22:26,599
When can we have a baby?

754
00:22:29,079 --> 00:22:29,960
Any time.

755
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:32,440
We're in charge of our own lives.

756
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:32,920
Fine.

757
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:36,160
But preferably next year.

758
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,839
No later than the year after.

759
00:22:54,039 --> 00:22:55,359
You need to make up for your brother.

760
00:22:56,640 --> 00:22:57,240
I didn't say anything.

761
00:22:58,440 --> 00:22:59,480
And I've been doing this

762
00:22:59,799 --> 00:23:00,960
with you, right?

763
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:04,000
Wenwen is your brother's daughter.

764
00:23:05,079 --> 00:23:05,759
When we took

765
00:23:05,759 --> 00:23:06,720
Wenwen in,

766
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:09,640
we gave her the best food,

767
00:23:09,759 --> 00:23:11,400
the best clothes, everything.

768
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:15,039
I never complained, did I?

769
00:23:17,279 --> 00:23:18,480
About her private school,

770
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:19,640
I told you

771
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,680
it wasn't necessary.

772
00:23:21,279 --> 00:23:22,240
But you insisted.

773
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,319
120,000 a year.

774
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:25,680
I gritted my teeth and paid for it.

775
00:23:26,599 --> 00:23:27,599
I never said a word.

776
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:28,359
Right?

777
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,640
Your mother calls me a stepmother.

778
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:31,799
Says I'm evil.

779
00:23:34,279 --> 00:23:35,119
She even wrote names

780
00:23:35,599 --> 00:23:37,079
on eggs so I couldn't eat them.

781
00:23:37,079 --> 00:23:38,160
(Wen)
Who’s evil here?

782
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:40,000
(Wen)
How can they treat me like this?

783
00:23:41,319 --> 00:23:42,559
I'm really at my limit, Yu Ming.

784
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:44,279
You can understand that, can't you?

785
00:23:48,799 --> 00:23:50,240
Your mother made you kneel and swear

786
00:23:50,799 --> 00:23:52,240
not to have a child

787
00:23:52,319 --> 00:23:53,400
before Wenwen started kindergarten.

788
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:55,240
And I agreed.

789
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:58,279
Then she said after elementary school.
I said fine.

790
00:24:00,480 --> 00:24:01,279
After elementary school,

791
00:24:01,759 --> 00:24:02,640
she said middle school.

792
00:24:04,119 --> 00:24:05,480
Three more years.

793
00:24:06,119 --> 00:24:07,400
Then high school.

794
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:10,119
Then college.

795
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:11,640
How old am I, Yu Ming?

796
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,519
Do I really need to remind you?

797
00:24:16,119 --> 00:24:16,920
I'm 36.

798
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:19,880
If I wait any longer,
I may never have a child.

799
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:23,240
I just want to ask you.

800
00:24:24,680 --> 00:24:25,519
When will this be an end

801
00:24:25,519 --> 00:24:26,559
for your family?

802
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,079
When will you

803
00:24:30,759 --> 00:24:31,359
finally get past

804
00:24:32,079 --> 00:24:33,119
your brother's death?

805
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,359
When will I get to live

806
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,359
a normal life?

807
00:24:35,359 --> 00:24:36,599
Just give me a date.

808
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:37,960
I'm sorry.

809
00:24:40,119 --> 00:24:40,799
I really want

810
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,319
a child of our own.

811
00:24:45,480 --> 00:24:46,079
For years now,

812
00:24:46,559 --> 00:24:47,920
you ask me

813
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:49,680
the same question almost every week.

814
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,720
and it always turns into a fight.

815
00:24:53,359 --> 00:24:53,799
I understand.

816
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,039
I’ve been avoiding it.

817
00:24:56,839 --> 00:24:58,200
But today, I want to say...

818
00:25:01,119 --> 00:25:04,200
I really don't know. I...

819
00:25:10,319 --> 00:25:10,960
You're tired.

820
00:25:12,119 --> 00:25:13,000
Mom's tired.

821
00:25:13,599 --> 00:25:14,480
Dad's tired.

822
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:19,559
It's all my fault.

823
00:25:21,480 --> 00:25:23,240
Maybe I really am a jinx.

824
00:25:27,119 --> 00:25:28,440
If you're really tired…

825
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:32,079
maybe we should separate.

826
00:25:47,079 --> 00:25:47,920
Let me try the shoes on.

827
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,599
Finally, you bought shoes that fit.

828
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:01,039
Comfortable?

829
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:05,680
Tomorrow morning at ten.

830
00:26:07,079 --> 00:26:07,640
What for?

831
00:26:08,559 --> 00:26:09,759
Civil Affairs Bureau, divorce papers.

832
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:12,759
Why?

833
00:26:12,799 --> 00:26:14,079
What's wrong with you, Yu Ming?

834
00:26:14,359 --> 00:26:15,160
Have you lost your mind?

835
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:19,640
Bring your ID.

836
00:26:58,839 --> 00:26:59,960
I just want to ask you something.

837
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:01,680
When will you

838
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:02,880
finally get past

839
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,480
your brother's death?

840
00:27:04,599 --> 00:27:05,720
When will I get to live

841
00:27:05,839 --> 00:27:06,720
a normal life?

842
00:27:06,759 --> 00:27:08,000
Just give me a date.

843
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:09,240
Watch out!

844
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:26,880
Brother.

845
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,240
Brother.

846
00:27:29,039 --> 00:27:29,799
Wake up.

847
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:31,799
Sister-in-law.

848
00:27:43,960 --> 00:27:45,480
I'm sorry, mom.

849
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,039
It's all because of me.

850
00:27:47,039 --> 00:27:48,400
I killed my brother
and sister-in-law.

851
00:27:50,519 --> 00:27:51,559
I'll raise Wenwen

852
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,960
as if she were

853
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,400
my own daughter.

854
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:00,319
Are you looking for mom?

855
00:28:00,839 --> 00:28:01,240
Is that it?

856
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,079
Do you want mom?

857
00:28:05,119 --> 00:28:06,440
Here, hold it.

858
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:08,480
Come here.

859
00:28:09,039 --> 00:28:09,480
It's okay.

860
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:10,440
She just keeps crying.

861
00:28:10,519 --> 00:28:11,599
Mommy's here.

862
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,119
It's okay. Don't be scared.

863
00:28:14,039 --> 00:28:14,720
It's okay, it's okay.

864
00:28:14,720 --> 00:28:15,400
Stop crying now.

865
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:16,400
Give me that.

866
00:28:16,519 --> 00:28:17,359
Try to cheer her up.

867
00:28:17,519 --> 00:28:17,759
Okay.

868
00:28:18,759 --> 00:28:19,119
Come on.

869
00:28:19,119 --> 00:28:19,319
Look.

870
00:28:19,759 --> 00:28:20,160
Take a sip.

871
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:20,880
