00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:49,920
Let me get up first.

1157
00:41:50,199 --> 00:41:51,360
There are people all around.

1158
00:41:51,559 --> 00:41:53,280
Things get exaggerated so easily online.

1159
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:54,800
If someone films this

1160
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:55,400
and posts it online,

1161
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,519
it won't be good for you.

1162
00:41:56,639 --> 00:41:58,639
I've done nothing wrong.

1163
00:41:59,199 --> 00:42:00,760
Let them film it. Let them post it.

1164
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:02,679
Let me try this.

1165
00:42:03,119 --> 00:42:04,159
This one's no ice.

1166
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,119
Get up.

1167
00:42:13,800 --> 00:42:15,280
Come with me to the bank

1168
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,719
and give me my 200,000,

1169
00:42:17,039 --> 00:42:17,480
or...

1170
00:42:17,599 --> 00:42:18,800
I'm taking you to the police station.

1171
00:42:19,119 --> 00:42:19,599
No.

1172
00:42:20,039 --> 00:42:21,320
Why go to the police station?

1173
00:42:21,719 --> 00:42:22,840
Why trouble the officers

1174
00:42:22,840 --> 00:42:23,559
with things like this?

1175
00:42:24,920 --> 00:42:25,679
How about this, Ming?

1176
00:42:26,239 --> 00:42:27,559
Will you trust me just one more time?

1177
00:42:27,559 --> 00:42:28,320
No.

1178
00:42:28,599 --> 00:42:28,800
I...

1179
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,639
I'll take you somewhere special.

1180
00:42:30,719 --> 00:42:31,519
I'm not going.

1181
00:42:32,519 --> 00:42:33,519
Yu Ming, why are you

1182
00:42:33,920 --> 00:42:34,679
so stubborn?

1183
00:42:35,280 --> 00:42:35,800
Fine.

1184
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:37,280
Twelve years ago,

1185
00:42:37,519 --> 00:42:38,440
you wanted to be a singer.

1186
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:39,880
You asked me to help you
put out an album.

1187
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:41,480
And yes,

1188
00:42:41,519 --> 00:42:42,519
I gave your 200,000 yuan

1189
00:42:42,519 --> 00:42:43,039
to someone else.

1190
00:42:43,239 --> 00:42:44,159
They failed,

1191
00:42:44,199 --> 00:42:45,159
so you can't

1192
00:42:45,159 --> 00:42:45,800
come after me alone.

1193
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:46,519
No.

1194
00:42:46,559 --> 00:42:46,760
Well...

1195
00:42:47,519 --> 00:42:47,920
Yu Ming.

1196
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:48,920
Seriously.

1197
00:42:48,960 --> 00:42:50,119
Just trust me one last time.

1198
00:42:50,719 --> 00:42:52,239
One last time.

1199
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,480
I'll show you something worth 6 million.

1200
00:42:55,840 --> 00:42:56,679
Come take a look.

1201
00:42:57,119 --> 00:42:58,239
After that, you can decide.

1202
00:42:58,280 --> 00:42:58,880
If it doesn't work

1203
00:42:59,079 --> 00:43:00,199
take me to the police then.

1204
00:43:00,719 --> 00:43:01,079
Deal?

1205
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:09,880
(Next Episode)

1206
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:10,239
(Guo Jingfei)

1207
00:43:10,239 --> 00:43:11,519
(Guo Jingfei)
Hi, I'm Guo Jingfei.

1208
00:43:11,519 --> 00:43:13,960
(Guo Jingfei)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

1209
00:43:13,960 --> 00:43:14,120
(Guo Jingfei)

1210
00:43:14,480 --> 00:43:15,519
This is the best villa community

1211
00:43:15,639 --> 00:43:17,039
around here.

1212
00:43:17,840 --> 00:43:18,679
One million.

1213
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:19,719
Give me a chance

1214
00:43:20,079 --> 00:43:21,199
