1215
00:43:22,800 --> 00:43:24,559
Congratulations, Xinlu!

1216
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:25,440
The Greentown project.

1217
00:43:25,440 --> 00:43:26,079
You know how much work

1218
00:43:26,079 --> 00:43:27,239
I put into that project.

1219
00:43:27,400 --> 00:43:28,800
She can just snatch it so casually,

1220
00:43:28,800 --> 00:43:30,599
and feel fine?

1221
00:43:32,880 --> 00:43:33,360
Hello?

1222
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:34,519
I need a loan.

1223
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:35,679
What's your collateral?

1224
00:43:36,239 --> 00:43:36,719
My apartment.

1225
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:39,079
You pledge the property deed. I transfer the money.

1226
